OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny early mist quickly clearing
OL,6,Fto leave a generally dry and bright
OL,7,Fday with plenty of sunny spells and
OL,8,Flight winds. An isolated light shower
OL,9,Fis possible in the afternoon, mainly
OL,10,Fin the east. Feeling very warm and
OL,11,Fincreasingly humid.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FAny showers easing to leave a
OL,14,Fdry night with clear spells and light
OL,15,Fwinds for all. Feeling rather warm and
OL,16,Fmuggy, especially in urban areas
OL,17,Ftowards the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
