OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FA little showery rain is
OL,6,Fpossible for a time in the west, but
OL,7,Fgenerally dry and bright with sunny
OL,8,Fspells for most of us. Feeling hot and
OL,9,Fhumid for many.
